name: Dry Chilli Chicken
description: A fiery delight straight form Asian cuisine, chilli chicken is a popular one across age groups! With a hint of chillies and a mix of spices, this one is unmissable!

name: Peri Peri Chicken Satay
description: Boneless chicken chunks, marinated in a pool of spices and grilled to perfection, this chicken satay is a must-try

name: Paneer 65
description: Made with cubes of paneer cheese that are marinated in spices and pan fried to perfection

name: Chicken Kebab
description: Dish of Middle Eastern or Central Asian origin that typically combines small pieces of meat vegetables on a skewer and is then grilled

name: Chicken Popcorn
description: A perfect snack for a movie night with friends and family, crunchy and crispy chicken popcorns are a quick, easy and absolutely delicious mix of chicken chunks rolled in cornflour, eggs, red chilli powder and bread crumbs, fried till golden

name: Chicken Sukka
description: It is a flavourful combination of a host of spices, freshly grated coconut and just two tablespoons of oil! The addition of special masala called Kundapur masala powder in the delicacy makes it a satisfying chicken treat!
